<paragraph blockId="27.[168,775,764,1397]" pageId="27" pageNumber="1030">
Therophytes, native with distribution in the Southern Cone Region of South Americ; previously recorded in 
<collectingRegion box="[168,411,1006,1030]" country="Argentina" name="Buenos Aires" pageId="27" pageNumber="1030">Buenos Aires province</collectingRegion>
but not in mountain range areas.
</paragraph>
